{"lemma":"أَعْوَصَيْ","slug":"أَعْوَصَيْ","root":"ع.#.ص","root_slug":"ع-_-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-_-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31009","n31014"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%92%D9%88%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31009","headword_ar":"اَعْوَصَ","root":"EwS","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He said what was difficult to be understood:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he spoke,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made use of, strange language,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a strange expression."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) [See also 2.] You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEwS fiY AlmanoTiqi","text_ar":"اعوص فِى المَنْطِقِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was obscure in speech."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEwS biAlxaSomi","text_ar":"اعوص بِالخَصْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, O, K,) inf. n. [or rather quasi-inf. n.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawaSN","text_ar":"عَوَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiyaASN","text_ar":"عِيَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA, [the latter written in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayAS","text_ar":"عَياص"},{"kind":"text","text":",])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made the adversary's case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair, difficult and intricate to him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he brought upon the adversary that which was difficult and intricate to him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he brought the adversary into a case which he did not understand."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEwS Ealayohi","text_ar":"اعوص عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He introduced against him, of arguments, what it was difficult for him to evade."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEowaSaniY","text_ar":"اَعْوَصَنِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It caused me to be in difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"so that I was unable to accomplish it]. (Ibn-'Abbád, in O voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEowaqa","text_ar":"اَعْوَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","S","A","O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n31014","headword_ar":"اَعْوَصُ","root":"EwS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawoSaA='u","text_ar":"عَوْصَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawiySN","text_ar":"عَوِيصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", throughout."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}